data.description:
Mother In Law suite / Apartment !!!
Beautiful Custom Built Home on 3 .09 acres with   mature Magnolias and Oak Trees .This Home features 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths .The  Kitchen has two dining areas, custom cabinets, granite countertops, tile backsplash and SS appliances .The living room has built-in bookshelves that surround a  gas log fireplace. Primary bedroom suite is on the first floor. The upstairs has a game room with a pool table , 3 bedrooms and a full bath. 
Above the Garage is a separate Apartment/Mother In Law suite  with a Large living area, Kitchen/Dining area,  bedroom and full-bath .The Apartment has its own private entrance.

Welcome home to your private Oasis, Walk out from the sunroom onto your own outdoor living space which has several setting areas for entertaining and enjoy the Salt Water Pool. Have a drink at the Tikki  Bar and  then enjoy the outdoor Hot Tub. With tons of outdoor lighting for evening cookouts or relaxing by the pool after work . The Pool house has storage space and a Bathroom. The Home was painted on the outside last year and gutters were replaced .The interior of the Home was  just painted .The front door was just sanded and re stained The roof was replaced 3 years old. The pool Salt System Control Panel was replaced last year.
Just a few miles from town squares dining , entertainment and shopping. Home has a  detached Mother in Law Suite / Apartment  full Kitchen , full bath , living space is 670 square feet.
